# Бой

**FSM:** choice(~5s roulette) → ready(button) → countdown(5s) → play → explosion → ready|result. First card: `next_card()` end of countdown if null. After boom: next_card→next_player→ready.

**UI init trap:** FSM starts in `initialize()` before child `_ready`. HUD + `game_input` MUST `_sync_to_current_state()` in `_ready`.

**Layout:** `BackgroundBomb` + `MenuBombLayout`/`GameBombBackground` (`Background.png`, cover 1080×1920). Battle UI in `ScaledContent` design coords. Markers: `PlayerName` (name plate + lighten overlay), `RoundWord` (syllable/countdown on dial). No round bomb sprite.

**HUD** (`game_hud.gd`, accent `#F5470A`): PlayerStrip@`PlayerName` · SyllableCard@`RoundWord` · ActionHints(y~1120) · countdown@`RoundWord` · explosion overlay · ResultPanel (screen). No edge vignette.

State UI: choice=«Выбираем первого»+pulse · ready=«Первым ходит»+StartRoundButton · play=full HUD · explosion=name overlay.

**Input** (`game_input.gd`): `mouse_filter=IGNORE`. PLAY: tap→next, swipe→prev (1×/round). RESULT→menu. StartRoundButton: `BackgroundBomb/ScaledContent/StartRoundButton`.

**Visual:** `GameBombBackground` (Control: `PlayerColorBackground` under `BombArt`) — player-color backdrop via `SlimeColors`, alert pulse on bg, bomb-only flash/shake on explosion · particles at (540,1050).

**Audio:** game_sound on PLAY only → audio.mdc.

**Core:** `game_manager.gd` `game_session.gd` `game_sound.gd` `word_condition.gd`
